		On-Site Wedding Amenities







Bridal Suite with Kitchen, private bathroom, and quaint outdoor sitting area
Catering Prep Kitchen
Deck Patio on the side of building, perfect for hosting cocktail hour
Groom and Groomsmen prep area with private bathroom
4 Large Boxwood walls
275 Custom Wooden Rattan Chairs
Farm and Folding Tables
Lounge Seating included on lower level
Steel Bentwood Cafe chairs on patio
Interchangeable chandeliers in main event space
Access to wifi for guests
Restroom on upper and lower levels
ADA compliant facility on main and lower levels
On-site Parking












		Venue Capacity








		We know each wedding is unique and we love that we can provide accommodations for a variety of visions. Whether our couples are looking for an intimate wedding for 50, or a large celebration of 200+, we have the ability to accommodate many different arrangements. The max venue capacity is three hundred persons; however, layout and wedding set preferences will determine the seating capacity for each event. We are happy to guide you according to your needs!

